# SDLC Skills — Designer

## Your Skills (13)

### Design-to-Code (Figma MCP)
- `/design-to-code <figma-url>` — Translate a Figma design into production code
- `/design-token-sync <figma-url> --format tailwind` — Sync design tokens from Figma to codebase
- `/component-audit <figma-url>` — Audit component coverage between Figma and codebase
- `/visual-review <figma-url> --implementation path/to/component` — Compare UI against Figma design

### Specification
- `/spec-gen '<feature>'` — Generate structured spec from a feature request
- `/spec-review specs/NNN/spec.md` — Validate implementation matches spec
- `/user-story-refiner 'rough feature idea'` — Transform an idea into a structured user story

### Design Validation
- `/design-review [file-or-'full']` — Review architecture and design patterns
- `/api-contract-analyzer main` — Detect breaking API changes between versions

### Communication & Collaboration
- `/bug-report 'the export button does nothing'` — Generate a structured bug report from a description
- `/codebase-qa 'does our app support dark mode?'` — Ask questions about the codebase in plain English
- `/changelog-plain latest` — Translate technical changes into plain language

### Documentation
- `/doc-gen api` — Generate or update API documentation

## Your Pipelines (5)

### Design Implementation
Translate a Figma design into verified code:
```
/run-pipeline designer/design-implementation https://figma.com/design/abc123/MyDesign?node-id=1-234
```
Chain: design-to-code → component-audit → design-to-code → visual-review → design-token-sync

### Design System Sync
Synchronize tokens and audit component coverage:
```
/run-pipeline designer/design-system-sync https://figma.com/design/abc123/DesignSystem
```
Chain: design-token-sync → component-audit → design-token-sync → design-review

### Design Handoff
Prepare a design for engineering handoff:
```
/run-pipeline designer/design-handoff https://figma.com/design/abc123/MyDesign?node-id=1-234
```
Chain: design-to-code → spec-gen → spec-review → doc-gen

### Spec Collaboration
Validate design aligns with specification:
```
/run-pipeline designer/spec-collaboration specs/NNN/spec.md
```
Chain: spec-gen → spec-review

### Design Validation
Validate design implementation:
```
/run-pipeline designer/design-validation
```
Chain: design-review → api-contract-analyzer
